[h3]Conquerors! we bring you news of another sale, this time with a Twist...[/h3]
For a limited time, Europa Universalis 4 and Victoria 3 are bundling up to face the Autumn chills together! 

[b]This dynamic bundle is now offered on Steam here: [/b]
https://store.steampowered.com/bundle/46785/Gold_and_Glory/

Aside from Gold and Glory, we also wanted to highlight that Paradox Interactive is taking part in this years Autumn sale on Steam! With discounts up to 90% off.

[img]{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/4678173/9e0e74e2a5da4f7b27489f21b7e967be89373085.png[/img]
For new players new we highly recommend our [url=https://store.steampowered.com/sub/1134298/]starter edition[/url], currently [b]80% off. [/b]
If you're new also feel free to check out our [url=https://pdxint.at/EUIVResources]player resources[/url]

For collectors of all the DLC the [url=https://store.steampowered.com/bundle/22085/Europa_Universalis_IV_Ultimate_Bundle/]ultimate bundle[/url] might be more up your alley.

[b]If you're not interested in bundles, you can also find our individual DLCs discounted below:[/b]
